    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's the perfect fit if you're looking for something reliable and smooth that still looks great on the road. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love how it handles. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
