    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 luxury SUV that perfectly balances sophisticated style with everyday utility. The Alpine White exterior retains a brilliant, deep gloss, and the vehicle has been exclusively garage-kept to protect the finish. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free Mocha Dakota leather interior that remains supple, with only very light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster consistent with careful use. All premium features, including the panoramic moonroof, heated front seats, and the high-resolution navigation system, are in full working order. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound; it features a complete service history performed at authorized centers, with a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection just completed. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia from highway commuting, the car presents beautifully and drives as smoothly as the day it was first driven off the lot. It is a reliable, high-quality choice for anyone seeking luxury without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning motorist. This unit has undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical performance and aesthetic presentation. Offering a refined driving experience and proven reliability, this vehicle stands as a testament to quality engineering and responsible ownership. We invite you to experience the superior handling and sophisticated appointments of this exceptional executive-class offering.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
