    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride and it's looking for a new home. It\u2019s been super well-loved and is in great shape for its next owner! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go and runs like a dream. I've taken good care of it, and I think you're really going to love how it handles. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
