      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The mechanical health is prioritized with a recently serviced VANOS unit and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain chassis integrity under load. It features a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery and a refreshed suspension setup utilizing Bilstein dampers for sharpened turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains exceptionally tight, pulling cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline with the distinct rasp of its individual throttle bodies.",
